HEADWORD: Inviscate
<hw>In*vis"cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Inviscated</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
